.\venv\Scripts\activate
uvicorn main:app --reload

Update the API URL in your app to use this IP address, e.g.:
http://<your-laptop-ip>:8000/upload/video
Run your backend with:
.\venv\Scripts\activate
uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
This makes the backend accessible from your phone.
Test from your phone:
Open the browser on your phone and try to access:
http://<your-laptop-ip>:8000/
If you see a response, the connection works.

